stylometry: Data mining is the act of gathering a set of data for review. It is taking a data set, and determining what attributes would best categorize the situation you are analyzing. It is important in business because it helps upper level management make business like decisions.  It can help them analyze past to present data, and understand if they have improved or worsened. It can also help when after data mining, if the company were to cluster the data, because then they could see what cluster the data falls into.  This is great for comparisons, and great to realize where improvement is needed.
